

 
Technical content:
 
		Title:  VMM on top   
 
		Objective: This example demonstrates a simple UVM-on-top environment, where UVM controls the phasing of UVM and any integrated VMM envs.

		Description:  
Class- my_uvm_env
 Top-level UVM container, which can later be reused as a block-level component.

	
		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	comp            -- To compile the design
        run             -- To run the design
        all             -- It does all the above steps.
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 

